    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document specifies a new extension for use in Mobile IPv4.  This extension can be added by the Home Agent and the Foreign Agent to Registration Reply messages.  This extension carries a text string that is intended for the user of the Mobile Node. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
